name: MXHangDiagnostic
desc: An object representing a diagnostic report for an app that is too busy to handle user input responsively.

items.name: var hangDuration: Measurement<UnitDuration>
items.desc: The amount of time the app is busy and unable to respond to user interaction.

items.name: var callStackTree: MXCallStackTree
items.desc: The call stack for the app hang report.
